    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 &quot;特工&quot;礼包</h2><br>“特工”武器套装里面的物品都能够消灭任何玩家遇到的敌人。世界上最强大的武器和独特自动手枪在一起可以帮你成为优秀战士。你的游戏 — 你的规定！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/2edcd74d7eee0425b222faeb6cd716c2.poster.avif?t=1685626390\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/2edcd74d7eee0425b222faeb6cd716c2.webm?t=1685626390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/2edcd74d7eee0425b222faeb6cd716c2.mp4?t=1685626390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>套装中有两把武器：合适任何职业（除了SED）的手枪，和“步枪手”职业自动抢。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/d77c65a0150d0ae41b58b90357d21ccd.poster.avif?t=1685626390\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/d77c65a0150d0ae41b58b90357d21ccd.webm?t=1685626390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/d77c65a0150d0ae41b58b90357d21ccd.mp4?t=1685626390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >H&amp;K USP</h2>该武器是一款由德国黑克勒&amp;科赫公司研制的半自动手枪。战士们都觉得这把武器超级可靠，任何战斗中能够帮你避免死亡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/30fc1cbed5ed3260edc216c226633bc4.avif?t=1685626390\" width=616 height=256 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Famas F1</h2>Famas F1 是法国设计制造的无托型突击步枪，也是法国陆军的现役步枪。武器腰射一定让你满意，此外武器还能过一次发射三个子弹。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/81f94c8989249121b75cf2007e0b17c7.avif?t=1685626390\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1700720/extras/bfad5e5a6b9e16e2537d7377c77db453.avif?t=1685626390\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>支付好之后请稍等15分钟左右。如果物品还没到账的话，请重新启动游戏。",
